# Walkthrough: Missing Content Fix + Premium Design Upgrade

## Phase 1: Missing Content Fixes

Fixed 3 root causes that made content invisible across all service pages:

### CSS — Added Missing Styles
Added CSS rules to [style.css](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/style.css) for `.timeline`, `.timeline-step`, `.timeline-dot`, `.timeline-content`, `.faq-container`, and `.faq-toggle` — classes used by service pages that had no matching CSS.

### JS — IntersectionObserver + FAQ Toggle
Added the full script block (fade-up observer + FAQ accordion) to:
- [llc-formation.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/llc-formation.html)
- [bank-assistance.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/bank-assistance.html)
- [itin-application.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/itin-application.html)
- [us-phone.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/us-phone.html)

### us-address-service.html Rebuild
Completely rewrote [us-address-service.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/us-address-service.html) from a broken Tailwind prototype to a native page matching the site's design.

