## Phase 2: Premium Design Upgrade (LLC Formation — Option B)

Used **UI/UX Pro Max** skill to generate a design system and apply premium CSS.

### Changes to [style.css](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/style.css)

| Upgrade | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Root variables** | Enabled glow shadows (`--shadow-glow-red/green/gold`), added `--gradient-hero` radial gradient, enhanced `--glass-border-hover` |
| **Hero glow** | Animated gold+purple radial orb (`heroGlow` keyframes, 8s ease-in-out infinite) |
| **Bento cards** | Golden top-line shimmer on hover, `cursor-pointer`, deeper box-shadow with gold glow |
| **Timeline dots** | Pulsing gold glow animation (`dotPulse` keyframes, 3s), golden hover on content cards |
| **Liquid glass** | Golden border tint + outer glow on hover |
| **FAQ** | Added `:hover` gold color, fixed duplicate `+` icon bug |
| **Accessibility** | Added `prefers-reduced-motion` media query |

### Changes to [llc-formation.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/llc-formation.html)
- Replaced CTA button emojis (🏢, 📞) with inline Lucide SVG icons

